flowchart TD
    %% ==================== MAIN SPINE ====================
    Start([START]) 
        --> Ingestion[TASK INGESTION]
        --> Orc[ORCHESTRATOR]
        --> Decomp[DECOMPOSE TASK INTO SUBTASKS]
        --> Assign[DELEGATE TO SPECIALIST AGENTS]

    %% ==================== SPECIALISTS POOL (explicit output nodes) ====================
    subgraph "SPECIALISTS POOL"
        direction LR
        Architect[ARCHITECT] -->|Designs| Design[Design]
        Toolsmith[TOOLSMITH] -->|Builds Tools| Tools[Tools]
        Implementer[IMPLEMENTER] -->|Implements| Implementation[Implementation]
        Tester[TESTER] -->|Tests| Testing[Testing]
        Reviewer[REVIEWER] -->|Reviews| Review[Review]
    end

    Assign --> SpecialistsPool[" "]
    SpecialistsPool --> Monitor[PROGRESS MONITOR]

    %% ==================== MONITORING & CONTROL ====================
    subgraph "MONITORING & CONTROL"
        Sec[SECRETARY] 
            -->|Audits| Audit[AUDITS]
        Sec 
            -->|Detects Silence| SilenceQ{SILENCE 10-20 min?}
        
        SilenceQ 
            -->|YES| Prio[PRIORITY RE-ADJUSTMENT]
        Prio 
            -->|Re-route to Orchestrator| Orc
    end

    %% ==================== MAIN MONITORING LOOP ====================
    Monitor 
        --> Check{ALL SUBTASKS<br>COMPLETE?}

    Check 
        -->|NO| Monitor
    Check 
        -->|YES| Delivery[FINAL DELIVERY]

    Delivery 
        --> ReviewC[REVIEW CYCLE]

    %% Review Cycle branches (full feedback loop)
    ReviewC 
        --> Approved{ }
    Approved 
        -->|APPROVED| Complete([TASK COMPLETE])
    Approved 
        -->|REVISIONS NEEDED| Orc

    %% ==================== TIMEOUT DETECTION (bottom subsystem) ====================
    subgraph "TIMEOUT DETECTION"
        TimeoutQ{TIMEOUT DETECTED?} 
            -->|YES| Advisor[TIMEOUT ADVISOR]
        Advisor 
            -->|Consult| Orc
    end

    %% ==================== LAYOUT HELPERS (keeps Monitoring on right + Timeout at bottom) ====================
    Monitor ~~~ MonitoringGroup[" "]
    MonitoringGroup ~~~ TimeoutGroup[" "]

    %% ==================== STYLING ====================
    classDef process fill:#0a0a0a,stroke:#00ff41,color:#00ff41,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#0a0a0a,stroke:#ffcc00,color:#ffcc00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef complete fill:#0a0a0a,stroke:#00ff41,color:#00ff41,stroke-width:3px,font-weight:bold
    classDef subgraphTitle fill:#1a1a1a,color:#00ff41,stroke:#00ff41

    class Start,Ingestion,Orc,Decomp,Assign,Delivery,ReviewC,Architect,Toolsmith,Implementer,Tester,Reviewer,Design,Tools,Implementation,Testing,Review,Audit,Prio,Advisor,Complete process
    class Check,SilenceQ,TimeoutQ,Approved decision
    class Complete complete
